The operating temperature for the IRB 140 is **+5°C (41°F) to +45°C (113°F)**.

When the ambient temperature is below 10°C, it is recommended to warm up the robot before use. This is because low temperatures can affect the viscosity of the oil and grease, which may impact the robot's performance.

